{"TopicId":141191,"ForumId":44,"TopicTitle":"Is it really this easy?","CreatedByName":"G\u0026#039;th","CreatedById":98595,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-04T15:42:08Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"G\u0026#039;th","CreatedById":98595,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-04T15:42:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo, whilst trolling google images becuase boredom, I came across this image:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://memeblender.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/troll-science-meme-magnet-wind-turbines.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022troll-science-meme-magnet-wind-turbines.\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd a thought occurs. Does this actually work? Logically my mind says no, and even if it did move it\u0027d eventually stop anyway, I would think. \u00A0Intuitively though, my mind is saying well of course it works, duh!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSomeone with a bit more knowledge on magnetism weigh in on this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-04T15:44:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAll I needed to see was the trollface and knew it was not possible.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso: If it worked, we\u0027d no longer be burning oil for most everything ever. And we\u0027d all live in a Utopia.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-06-04T15:52:19Z\u0022 title=\u002206/04/2016 03:52  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EJune 4, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by 5thHorseman\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"insert_name","CreatedById":150339,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-04T15:48:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo, the magnets are pulled towards the turbine as well, net torque would be 0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HebaruSan","CreatedById":156657,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-04T15:53:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nReplace the magnets with rubber bands that exert the same amount of pull between the same parts. All they do is try to compress the structure, not rotate it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"PB666","CreatedById":107380,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-04T15:53:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222616140\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022141191\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221465054928\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002298595\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022G\u0027th\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 minutes ago, G\u0027th said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo, whilst trolling google images becuase boredom, I came across this image:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022troll-science-meme-magnet-wind-turbines.\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://memeblender.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/troll-science-meme-magnet-wind-turbines.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd a thought occurs. Does this actually work? Logically my mind says no, and even if it did move it\u0027d eventually stop anyway, I would think. \u00A0Intuitively though, my mind is saying well of course it works, duh!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSomeone with a bit more knowledge on magnetism weigh in on this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd you believed that because of the big sarcastic looking face?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes it can work if the magnets are attached to a separate\u00A0\u00A0bar and you are the one\u00A0turning it not the wind.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"G\u0026#039;th","CreatedById":98595,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-04T15:57:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust to set the record straight, I knew the image was a joke, my curiosity was just piqued as to exactly why it didn\u0027t work.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cubinator","CreatedById":150330,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-04T19:02:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222616158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022141191\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221465055850\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002298595\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022G\u0027th\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, G\u0027th said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust to set the record straight, I knew the image was a joke, my curiosity was just piqued as to exactly why it didn\u0027t work.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s because while the magnets do pull on the turbine blades, the blades are also pulled towards the magnets with an equal amount of force. Thus, the whole thing would just compress slightly and it would not rotate. It\u0027s the same reason you can\u0027t move a car by pushing on the dashboard. The dashboard is pushed forward, but you are pushed back into the seat equally so the net force is zero.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Elrond Cupboard","CreatedById":89596,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-04T20:05:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022kG8dA7l.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022563\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/kG8dA7l.png\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spaceception","CreatedById":152800,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-04T21:32:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMoar;\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022tumblr_lbmorxvlcv1qzk6q6o1_500.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022https://27.media.tumblr.com/tumblr_lbmorxvlcv1qzk6q6o1_500.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022troll-science-levitation_20120524203442.\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://fakeplus.com/pictures/jpg/troll-science-levitation_20120524203442.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022b9908ea385d90d155bbd1a6568cc236d.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://trollscience.com/image/f/full/b9908ea385d90d155bbd1a6568cc236d.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022641849967.jpg?385\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://venom-blade.weebly.com/uploads/6/0/7/8/6078622/641849967.jpg?385\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI could go on as long as these exist \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bill Phil","CreatedById":127797,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-04T22:07:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222616158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022141191\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221465055850\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002298595\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022G\u0027th\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, G\u0027th said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust to set the record straight, I knew the image was a joke, my curiosity was just piqued as to exactly why it didn\u0027t work.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOnr magnet pulls one blade towards it. The other does the same.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA force is being applied, but it\u0027s canceled out by the other magnet applying force.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}